name: DevFest 2018 Ikorodu
description:
DevFest is our annual all-day developer conference that offers speaker sessions across multiple product areas and interests! We are excited to bring the DevFest18 energy to Ikorodu this year! We would be showcasing multiple speaker sessions in multiple google products area such as:
Google Cloud
Web
Mobile
Internet of Things (IoT)
Open-source etc
how_to_find_us: 58B Lagos road behind Access Bank, Opposite UBA, Benson bus-stop, Ikorodu, Lagos

name: Cloud Study Jam
description:
Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin? Join us at GDG Ikorodu for our Cloud Study Jam!
Get official Google training that is worth more than $55 in value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with the Cloud Console, Kubernetes, Security, IoT on Cloud, and Machine Learning.
Then after our Cloud Study Jam live session, you will have free access to more labs that you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to complete any labs you want.

Requirements?
What we only require from you is to bring your laptop and charger (PC, Mac or Chromebook)! The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers.

For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Firefox or Chrome installed.
Once again...... Donâ€™t forget your charger.

Cheers!!!
how_to_find_us: From Benson bus-stop, Ikorodu, cross to the other side of the road. Pass beside the Access bank. The event center is just behind Access bank.
